isplayCapabilities.canPresent</code></a> が&nbsp;<code>true の場合は1でなければなりません，</code>それ以外は&nbsp;0 です．</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">TBD.</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-vrdisplaycapabilities-maxlayers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"ja\">maxLayers の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">不明</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.VRDisplayCapabilities.maxLayers","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayCapabilities/maxLayers/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参照","title":"参照","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API homepage</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"http://mozvr.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MozVr.com</a> — Mozilla VRチームのデモ，ダウンロード，その他のリソース．</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"シンタックス","id":"シンタックス"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性"},{"text":"参照","id":"参照"}],"summary":"VRDisplayCapabilities インターフェイスの maxLayers 読取専用プロパティは，そのVRディスプレイが同時に表示できる VRLayer の最大値を示す数値を返します（例えば Display.requestPresent() が受け取ることのできる配列の最大長です)．","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"VRDisplayCapabilities.maxLayers","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/vrdisplaycapabilities/maxlayers","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/vrdisplaycapabilities/maxlayers/index.html","